credit_line: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
title: Birdcage
medium: Painted wood, painted metal, metal wire, glass
description: Square shaped wooden box painted black and red, with thin, vertical metal rods at front; out-curved door projecting from center, hinged on left side; two molded, clear glass bottles attached to rods on either side of door; scrolling cornice at top, with applied gold-painted metal coat of arms in center.  Woodwork has carved dentate edges and projections; two stepped, ovoid front feet, square rear feet.
name: Birdcage
